### NATS Client API Testing

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/nats/health

### 2. Test Echo (Simple Request-Response)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/nats/test/echo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hello NATS!",
  "metadata": "test from REST API"
}

### 3. Test Timeout
POST http://localhost:8080/api/nats/test/timeout
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Test Error Handling
POST http://localhost:8080/api/nats/test/error
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Generic NATS Request
POST http://localhost:8080/api/nats/request
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject": "demo.user.create",
  "payload": {
    "username": "john_doe",
    "email": "john@example.com",
    "action": "create_user"
  }
}

### 6. Publish Message (Fire and Forget)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/nats/publish
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject": "api.notification.send",
  "payload": {
    "userId": "12345",
    "message": "Welcome to our service!",
    "type": "welcome"
  }
}

### 7. Get Request Status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/nats/status/{{requestId}}

### 8. Get Requests by Status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/nats/requests/SUCCESS

### 9. Get NATS Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/nats/statistics